# Day 17 – Agentforce and Enterprise AI

## Introduction

Artificial Intelligence (AI) is transforming how organizations operate by automating tasks, improving decision-making, and enhancing customer experiences. Salesforce Agentforce represents a new generation of AI-powered agents that can perform tasks, answer questions, and execute business processes using enterprise data and automation tools.

This document provides an overview of Agentforce, AI agent use cases, enterprise AI workflows, risks, and key learnings.

---

# Agentforce Summary

## What is Agentforce?

Agentforce is Salesforce's platform for creating and deploying AI-powered agents that can interact with users, understand requests, retrieve information, and perform actions across Salesforce applications.

Unlike traditional chatbots, Agentforce agents can reason through tasks, use enterprise data, execute workflows, and assist users in real business processes.

### Key Capabilities

* Natural language interaction
* Task automation
* Data retrieval
* Workflow execution
* Customer support assistance
* Sales and service automation
* Integration with Salesforce platform

### Benefits of Agentforce

* Faster response times
* Increased productivity
* Reduced manual work
* Improved customer experiences
* Better decision support

